Link : https://code4rena.com/reports/2022-07-golom/#low-risk-and-non-critical-issues:~:text=%5BL%E2%80%9104%5D%20require()%20should%20be%20used%20instead%20of%20assert()

it is suggested even in the solidity documentation that assert should only be used for high criticality bugs. 
Small  errors or even inputs errors should not be included in assert 